products.description: This traditional oriental floral design is a classic pattern updated with tasteful modern touches to suit any space. The dominant green sage base is bordered by an intricate floral border to complete this traditional design machine made in Italy. Made of heat-set polypropylene, this rug provides a soft, non-shedding, durable, and easy-to-clean accent to the decor in your entryway, hallway, bedroom, playroom, dining room, or living room. A wide array of sizes and shapes, including rectangles, rounds, and runners, allows this machine-made rug collection to fit in any space comfortably. Rug Size: Rectangle 3'3" x 4'11"

Crafted from solid wood, this bench features a curved Windsor back with delicate slats, rolled arms, and a rectangular seat. We love that this bench's 44'' footprint provides a seat for two on your porch or in your sunroom, just right for entertaining guests. Plus, its traditional look blends in with rustic and modern farmhouse styles.Hand-curated by Kelly Clarkson. Color: Antique Black
